> > SUBROUTINE polps(a,s1,s2) ! Apply series A to scalar S1 to obtain S2
> > !$$$  subprogram documentation block
> > !                .      .    . 
> > ! subprogram:    polps
> > !
> > !   prgrmmr:  
> > !
> > ! abstract:  Apply series A to scalar S1 to obtain S2
> > !
> > ! program history log:
> > !   2008-04-25  safford -- add subprogram doc block
